name: IndieArchive
tagline: archiving the web that the indieweb deems worth linking to
body:
IndieArchive is a [project](http://indiewebcamp.com/projects) to collaboratively grow an archive of pages [replied to](http://indiewebcamp.com/comment) (possibly also mentioned) in indie web [posts](http://indiewebcamp.com/posts).

Read more on the IndieWebCamp wiki:

[indiewebcamp.com/IndieArchive](http://indiewebcamp.com/IndieArchive)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
